}
```

Expected result:
```
{
  "took": 4,
  "timed_out": false,
  "_shards": {
    "total": 1,
    "successful": 1,
    "skipped": 0,
    "failed": 0
  },
  "hits": {
    "total": {
      "value": 1,
      "relation": "eq"
    },
    "max_score": 2.6749716,
    "hits": [
      {
        "_index": "error-case",
        "_id": "2",
        "_score": 2.6749716,
        "_source": {
          "field1": [
            "If you say things to a person that turn out not to be true",
            "the person is inclined to think that he or she has been deceived."
          ]
        },
        "highlight": {
          "field1": [
            "If you say things to a person that turn out not <em>to</em> <em>be</em> <em>true</em>",
            "<em>the</em> <em>person</em> is inclined to think that he or she has been deceived."
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

The error does not occur if `require_field_match: false` is set or if `nested queries` are used.
The error started occurring from version 8.10.0, with version 8.9.2 being the last one that works correctly.

I think it is related to the change #96068 , where I also [wrote a comment](https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/pull/96068#issuecomment-2640030560).

### Steps to Reproduce

These tests are performed in version 8.17.0. But the same issue also occurs in version 8.10.0

https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/pull/96068#issuecomment-2640030560

